data.description: A must see!!! Gorgeous brick home on 22+ acres, fenced 10 acre pasture for horses, 2 stables, 2 acre pond, barn, workshop, partially finished basement, beautiful setting with awesome views, large rooms throughout, hardwood floors, huge deck, this home has so much to offer!! Great location, only min to HWY 75 and Griffin. Country living at its best! Possible owner financing.
